steps.description:
* Accept Quest: "Stealing Knowledge
* GO east accept A Meeting with the Master
* Find the Tablets
* Go East

*  Go back to Valormok at Jediga  (23, 51)
*

* Turn in Quest, Accept all 4 new Quests from Jediga
* Go east, Kill Hippogrypth for 2 Undamaged Hippogrypth Feathers.
* go up the Path, go up the Tower, Turn in Quest, Go down the tower, go down the path, 
* let u port back down.
* Go back in the camp, turn in quest
* fly to Thunder Bluff

* Turn in Quest in Elders Rise, 
* Fly to OG

* BANK GET: Dran's Ripple Delivery.
* Turn in Quests,
* Accept: "Jes'rimon's Payment to Jediga" + "Bone-Bladed Weapons"
* Leave OG Fly to UC
steps.tips: * learn new Spells if u need.

steps.description:
* go SouthWest Apothecarium, Turn in Tablet Quest, Accept next part
* go underground, accept Seeping Corruption, Turn instantly in!, accept new quest,
* turn in Tauren, go to Cuely Turn in quest.
* turn in "Return to apothecary zinge" (50.68).  Accept "Vivian Lagrave"
* Fuely: accept both quests!
* GO to the Flight Master, fly to Revantusk Village, The Hinterlands

* on the docks accept "Snapjaws, Mon!" and "Gammerita, Mon!"
* on the Hut the Dancing troll: Accept "The Final Message to the Wildhammer"
* in the Inn and accept "Lard Lost His Lunch"
* GO north and at the shore, KILL Turtles + Loot quest ITEMS on the ground (Bottles)
* look for elite Turtle, kill & loot quest item

* Dive down in front of the waterfall, loot Chest,
* swim on the tiny island loot Basket, kill trolls (loot ITEMS)
* Go the Path up

* Loot Mushroom in the Lake
* GO East

* use Final Message to the Wildhammer on the Fountain
* Go Back to Revantusk Village and turn in ALL QUESTS
* Move to Valormok, Azshara (other Continent)
* Turn in Quests, Fly to ratchet

* BIND YOURSELF IN RATCHET
* IN FRONT of the Hut there is a little chest, LOOT ITEM
* go into hut, accept Quest from Liv Rizzlefix
* PUT BANK:  Violet Tragan and Stone Circle
* GO to Booty Bay
* TURN IN all Quest you have in BB.
* fly to Stonard, Swamp of Sorrows

* GO south into Blasted Lands, Accept on the Side the Quest from the Dead Orc
* Go south to the Bloodelfs, Accept all 5 quests

* Blasted Land Grind, KILL EVERY BOAR, BIRD, BASILISK, HYENA, Skopion
* Vulture Gizzards 28 = 14 + 12 + 2
* Basilisk Brain 33 = 11 + 11 + 11  (MARKED WITH RED B)
* Blasted Boar Lungs 16 = 6 + 5 + 5
* Scorpok Pincers 12 = 6 + 3 + 3
* Snickerfang Jowls 13 = 5 + 5 + 3
* Kill mobs (RED DOTS), use before the title Obelisk stones.
* If everything is done, turn in Quests and Leave Area and, at the way out
* Turn in quest at Orc ghost, accept new + turn in other side of the street, accept new
* interact with Chest, (skip last quest: Kirith)
* HS back to Ratchet.
steps.tips: * if u find Dreanethyst Fragment / Sphere Turn in BLUE DOT

steps.description:
* At ratchet GET FROM BANK: Violet Tragan, Stone Circle
* fly to Gadgetzan, Tanaris.
* Turn in Quests, accept next parts, go to Noggerfogger, turn in quests, (Elixir grants no EXP)
* Leave South way

* Turn IN Quest, SKIP NEXT ONE (DUNGEON quest)
* GO to UN-GORO

* Accept all Quests
* Loot, te cadaver
* Grind north to the entrance of Marshal's Refuge

* Accept ALL QUEST
*get the Flight Point
* make yourself rdy for a BIG grind. (Inventory space, etc, Repair)
* Accept also the quest hidden near the graveYard, behind the stone ( /tar Larion )
* look down from the flight spot and you will see.
steps.tips: * Ignore the Blue quest, don't loot Bloodpetal Sprouts (NO EXP)

steps.description:
* Kill Tar Creeper / Beasts loot Items
* Kill the Bloodpetal flayers
* go up the hill, kill / Loot the  Pterrordax
* Go to the ape-Cave - kill all apes - Loot pelts

* Kill All Bloodpetal (plant NPC mobs)
* Loot Footstuffs (BLUE DOT)

* Kill/loot any Diemetradon for scales and bones.
* go to the Ungoro Entrance / turn in quests / accept new quests!
*

* Step over the Raptor Eggs, Kill spawned mob. Loot items
* Go to the ship wrack, interact, accept quests
* underwater in front of the wrack is "A Small Pack" DO NOT LOOT IT YET
* Go back to tauren / Turn in quest Accept next one
steps.tips: if your quest log is full, discard power Crystal Quest (4 power crystal color loot quest)

steps.description:
* Kill Gorishi Worker and other Silithus mobs, 
* go into the Cave (S), keep left until u enter a room, place yourself center use: Vial
* leave, go south to the Pterrordax (P) Kill all missing (loot all missing items)

* Loot the Research Equipment 
* kill all Bloodpetal Trapper,, Complete QUESTS (also complete bone quest!)
* work on Pterrordax Kill quest
* Accept new Quest. from the Goblin.
steps.tips:
* if quest log is full discard The quest from the Book u might found. 
* or discard: It's a Secret to Everybody

steps.description: * Complete "Beware of Pterrordax", "Shizzle's Flyer" and "Roll the Bones" + Larion and Muigin

* Kill FireElemenats for Ash + Core Of elements need 30 later
* Go On top of the Hill, At a geysir use the Thermometer!
* Grind Elementals until u have 30 Core of Elements
* go to the lower Cave, turn in quest.
* make the escort quest, sometimes the faint away, use water item in Inv.
* turn in ALL quests.
* go into CAVE, Accept quest and turn in (power stones), accept the 3 next parts (pylons

* GO up, activate the north Pylon
* go into the ape Cave, kill the BOSS ape (BROWN), loot quest Item
*

* Use the East Pylon, 
* east, the small stone plate one the ground, place the Preserved Threshadon Meat 
* use the Preserved Pheromone Mixture + Kill mob, loot item
*

* accept quest + Loot Items from the Pack, Destroy the Faded Photograph
* Turn in quest at the Tauren (East)

* get West Pylon 
* Go East Turn in quest and get new from the Goblin
* Go back to the Marshal's Refuge, TURN IN QUESTS in the Cave
* Fly to Gadgetzan, Tanaris
* TURN IN ALL QUESTS, don't accept anything new
steps.tips: * make sure you have 35 Un'goro Slime Samples and 30 Savage Fronds, at this Point!

steps.description:
* Go to the elders Rise
* Accept" Un'goro Soil", turn in on the North side of the giant tent
* go back and Accept: Morrowgrain Research,
* turn in south east side: SKIP NEXT PART
* Hearthstone to Ratchet!
* TURN IN QUESTS in Ratchet, SKIP "Zapper Fuel"
steps.tips: * Visit your Class Trainer.

steps.description:
* BANK GET: Black Dragonflight Molt + Dark Iron Scraps
* BANK PUT: Un'Goro soil, Un'goro Slime Samples, Savage Fronds, Linken's Training Sword,
** White Ravasaur Claws + ALL Core of Elements
* FLY to Kargath, Badlands

* Turn in Vivian Lagrave, skip next part
* accept: The Rise of the Machines.
* FROM the pat: accept Dreadmaul Rock (Troll)
* fly to the Flame Crest, Burning Steppes

* Accept ONLY: "Broodling Essence" and "Tablet of the Seven"
* Turn in quest, skip next Part.
* Go East, Use the Draco Quest Items on Scalding Broodling, Kill mob loot Essence. (RED DOT)

* in the cave Accept A Taste of Flame, and turn in: skip next Part.
* Go up the Dreadmaul Rock
* interact with the skeleton on the altar, 
* check All 3 Caves for Krom'Grul (LOOT nose ring from in)
steps.tips: * also Grind you 30 Dark Iron Scraps

steps.description:
* Kill Golems (War Reaver), Loot Item
* Read in front of the Stature the Stone tablet (inside the Ruin) (YELLOW DOT)
* Go back to Flame Crest (CAMP), Turn in Quests
* accept ONLY "Felnok Steelspring"
* Fly to Kargath, Badlands

* Turn in Rise of the Machines, accept next part
* turn in Nose Ring Quest
* go east, Turn in Rise of the Machines; SKIP next part
* Hearth to Ratchet
* PUT BANK: Dark Iron Scraps, Tinkee's Letter + ALL Core of Elements
* FLY TO ORGIMMAR, make OG your new HOME (HS)
* FLY TO Valormok, Azshara
steps.tips: * mages can port Directly to OG

steps.description:
* accept quest "Betrayed"
* Go North East, hill entrance (53, 20)
* Go up the Hill, accept "Kim'jael Indeed!"
* Do the Kim Jail Quest, Kill mobs + LOOT boxes on the ground until u find all items
** Compass, Scope, chicken, Wizzlegoober
* if all mobs down and Camp is found, go south east to the shore, there is a book and 3 stones
* use the book turn in quest/ accept next part, Use stone kill Mobs loot Quest mob head
* go back to Hill, turn in Quest, accept next part

* Kill Nagas unti a Rune dropped
* Go back on the Hill, Turn in Quest
* Go back to Valormok, turn in Quest, accept next Part
* Hearth to Orgrimmar
steps.tips:
* you should be 54 by now, u can grind the Bloodelfs 
* there have low Armor and 30% lower life pool, drop rune cloth

steps.description:
*BANK GET:  8 White Ravasaur Claws, Tinkee's Letter + Linken's Training Sword
* Turn in quests
* OPTIONAL: turn in cloth if u want.
* fly to Splintertree Post, Ashenvale
steps.tips:
* get also from the bank 60 Runecloth, for donations
* learn new skills if needed

steps.description: * Walk fast to Felwood
* Accept Quests.

* Kill all Slimes you will need 35 Felwood Slime Samples. (don't must be finished now)
* in the north way are more slimes + another quest
* GO north

* Kill Jaedenar Cultists and other mobs
* Kill Missing slimes (you need 35 Samples)
* On the way to the Camp, Kill missing slimes
* Accept all quests in camp

* Walk through one of the Crater to explore
* kill fire elementals (save the cores)

* Kill Grizzly and Ravengers (bears and Wolfes)
* go into the CAVE (RED C)
* kill mobs until u get 15 Blood Amber
* Go NorthEast

* Get quest at the Tunnel to Winterspring
* Kill mobs in the West
* Grind Deadwood until u are "2850 Hostile" (150 from unfriendly)
* Go back to the Tunnel, turn in quest, accept next part
* Go into the Tunnel, 
* On the Crossing, Keep NORTH go to moonglade
* get the Flight point on the west West side, after the exit!
* Go Back into the Tunnel Go to winter spring
steps.tips: * the Feather quest is a Rep only quest

steps.description:
* Turn in Quest, accept new Quests
* go south, ACCEPT QUEST IN CORRECT ORDER!
* first: accept: Threat of the Winterfall, 
* second: turn in quest The New Springs -> accept Strange Sources
* last Turn in: It's a Secret to Everybody -> don't wait for the npc, just leave
* Follow the main Street to Everlook

* Get Flight Point
* get in Everlook the quest on your left "Are We There, Yeti?"
* TURN in "Felnok Steelspring" quest: SKIP: Chillwind Horns
* BIND YOURSELF IN EVERLOOK (HS)
* get ALL QUESTs from the AGENT DAWN Npc's in the INN (3 in total)
* PUT BANK:  Blood Amber, Felwood Slime Samples, Everlook Report, 
** Studies in Spirit Speaking + ALL Core of Elements + Deadwood Ritual Totem (if u have it)
* GO south

* GO south until u discovers Strange Things
* HS back to Everlook

* Go East, kill Den Watcher
* kill all Raging Owlbeasts
* also Work on the kill/looting Ice Thistle Yeti quest.
* if u have all Raging owlbeasts slain -> next step!

* go east, kill Ragged Owlbeast
* kill Yeti loot items.
* Go south kill Winterfall Totemic + Pathfinder
* turn in quests, accept only "Falling to Corruption"
* Hearth (or go back) to Everlook
* Turn in Quest, accept next part of the yeti quest
steps.tips:
* Winterspring Activity (kill the Winterfall Ursas), is maybe turned In
** on the Entrance point (pserver stand)

steps.description:
* GO East; Kill Yeti, loot 2 Horns (Low drop rate)
* after finish, port or walk back, turn in quest accept next part
* Use quest item to Scare NPC near the INN (LEFT SIDE) ( /tar Legacki )
* Fly to Bloodvenom Post, Felwood

* Turn in Quest in Camp / skip NEXT part (for now)
* go south the main path 
* Turn in Quest by Maybess Riverbreeze (Tauren), Talk to her, get the [Cenarion Beacon]
* go to the other camp, south east, turn in quests: accept "Collection of the Corrupt Water"
* GO to the Timber, Grazzle, (NO MARK) accept quest
* go south

* Go south West, Kill ALL DEADWOODS, Loot shards
* Go to the south point kill Overlod Ror, Loot ITEM
* Go back to to Grazzle, turn in quest, accept other quest.
* if u have enough shards turn in, Get Item. 
* If u see a Corrupted plant, Interact!
* Go north

* Go WEST, stand into the Green Fountain, use "
* Go back on the main Street 
* a little bit north
* go to the Jaedenar Area, go into the Fountain, use "Empty Canteen"
* Go to the Bloodvenom Post, turn in Quests, accept "Corrupted Sabers"
steps.tips: * NEVER SELL THE Corrupted Soul Shards!

steps.description:
* by the Tauren on the way Turn in all Shards into "Plant Salve"
* Go south, turn in quests, skip Next part
* Go north to the Satyr Fountain
* Release Citten (Inv Item, Cage) into the Fountain. 
* Go back to the Bloodvenom Post (with big Murder Citten).
* Infornt of Winna Hazzard, Speak with Citten, Turn in Quest
* Leave Post, GO north to the Timber guys.

* Go north, kill all Deadwood 
* loot feathers, shards, Beads
* Go to the cooking pot, turn in quest, accept next
* go to the Tunnel to Winterspring
* turn in quests

* turn in quests, accept "Toxic horrors" from "Donova"
* Grind to lvl 56! at this point
* Hearthstone back to Everlook
* Accept in front of the INN (Harlo Wigglesworth), "A Little Luck", turn in east Everlook (Cages)
* Fly to OG
* Fly TO UnderCity
steps.tips: * IN OG you can get new spells.

steps.description:
* Accept from "Harbringer" -> Call to Arms: The Plaguelands! (Roams with a Latern around)
* Bind URSELF in UnderCity
* BANK PUT: Cenarion Beacon + Corrupted Soul Shards + Cenarion Plant Salves
* BANK GET: Felwood Slime Samples, Un'goro Slime Samples, Everlook Report
**  Studies in Spirit Speaking.  
* Go to the The Apothecarium, On the Table Near Chemist Fuely 
* use the 2 pots to convert the Slime Samples Open the item in Inv, 
* Repeat until u have 5 of both
* turn in quests, accept next part. DESTORY all remaining samples.
steps.tips: * Donate 60 extra Runecloth, if u want.

steps.description:
* Go back to the bank
* BANK PUT:  Encased Corrupt Ooze. 
* BANK GET: 30 Dark Iron Scraps / 30 Savage Fronds / 30 Core of Elements
* SEND the 90 Items to a Twink char, via Mail, AFTER a HOUR send it BACK. leave it in MAIL
* Leave undercity via, Elevator, go to The Bulwark (83, 70 in Tirisfal Glades)

* Turn in all quests,
* accept Scarlet Diversions, LOOT Box of Incendiaries next to the NPC, 
* wear the Argent Dawn Commission
* other side (south) ONLY accept: A Plague Upon Thee
* Go on the Field, Into the Left house Upstairs, accept quest.
* Go into the Barn, on the Ground Use Package Turn in quest 
* Use Package again accept quest
* Go West

* Kill all mobs at the Scarlet camp, Burn down the Tent (use click on it)
* SET THE BANNER near the Burned down TENT
* Go back to The Bulwark, 
* Turn in Quest: accept The Scourge Cauldrons
* turn in The Scourge Cauldrons, accept Target: Felstone Field
steps.tips: * Keep all Bone Fragments! you need many! (at least 30)

steps.description:
* Go to the First Field, Kill Cauldron Lord Bilemaw, Loot Key, 
* Use Scourge Cauldron, Turn in quest, accept next part
* go back to The Bulwark Turn in quest, accept next part.

* Go on the Field, Kill Cauldron Lord Malvinious, Loot key, use  Scourge Cauldron turn in/accept
* Go into the Barn, on the ground is a Book (Diary), Use it, accept quest
* Look for the " /tar Wand " Skeleton, loot key, unlock toilet chamber behind the barn
* kill spawn mob on toilet, loot key,
* go into the Farmhouse, second floor, use on the left side the Cabinet. turn in quest.
* Go back to The Bulwark, turn in quest, accept next part

* Go on the last Field, Kill Cauldron Lord Razarch, loot key, 
* use Scourge Cauldron
* go into the small house, talk to dead tauren
* accept quest
* Kill mobs until u have 30 Bone Fragments!
* go back to The Bulwark, Turn in quest, accept next part.

* GO to the last Field, kill Cauldron Lord Soulwrath,
* use  Scourge Cauldron, turn in and accept new quest.
* Go north to the Eastern Lands
* Accept All quests from Tirion Fordring

* Grind south
* accept all quest from Nathanos. (3 in total)
* go south into the crypt. lowest floor on the ground there is a scroll, accept quest!
* Go East, to Pamela, accept quest.

* Find Pamelas Doll
* the Parts are random in the Buildings.
* if u have all 3 parts, Combine then Together, and turn in quest by Pamela.
* Accept the next 2 quests.  
* Leave Darrowshire

* Kill all missing mobs
** kill 30 Plaguebats
** kill 20 Plaguehound Runts
** Kill/loot 15 Larves / Loot meat.
* finished go to Lights Hope, 
* Light's Hope Chapel (80, 64), accept "The Restless Souls" + "Zaeldarr the Outcast"
* turn in quests. Accept ONLY Defenders of Darrowshire!
* Other Side of the Camp A Human on a Horse "Dispath Commander Metz, Accept The Rooster
* Turn in Quest.
* Get Flight Point.
steps.tips: * DO NOT CONSUME Valor Token yet!

steps.description:
* Kill Banshees, Loot 7 Living Rot (FAST only last 10min)
* Combine 7 living rot with Mortar and Pestle
* work on: kill Gibbering Ghouls, talk to ghosts.
*  go North

* kill 5 Plaguehounds and 20 Noxious Plaguebats.
* grind your way North.

* Kill Bats + Hounds until finish.
* Go to the Gouls, (G) finish quest!
* Go North
* Go up the Path to the Trolls.

* Kill Infiltrator Hameya, Loot Key.
* Go West, Kill Bloodelves. kill all needed mobs
* Go into the Lounge, on the Right wing, ON A BENCH is a book, Loot the Register
* Go West
* Loot Termite Stocks around this area, Grind mobs (BLUE)

* to to the last Hut, Turn in Quest. skip next part (Instance Quest)
* Accept quest: Augustus' Receipt Book
* Go East.
steps.tips: * Kill Crypt Fiends and Loot, [Crypt Fiends Parts] - for an quest later

steps.description:
* Go into the INN (Largest Building).
* Go upstairs, and KEEP RIGHT, on the ground in the last room, is a book, Loot it.
* Bring him this book back 
* Grind 30 Crypt Fiend Parts. (grind on the ground about 20)
* if u have 20 parts, go through the Tunnel, ELITE LVL 60 INSIDE! PAT
* kill every mob

* Turn in all Quests, Accept new Quest.
* type in front of Tirion /sit, while sitting talk again to him listen to his story
* accept next part
* go south 
* Turn in Quests,
* Accept, "Oh How I hate Thee...", look northEast for DuskWing. (Elite NPC)
* if u don't find it, Abort quest
* go south.

* Go into the Crypt kill: Zaeldarr the Outcast, Loot HEAD
* Go behind the Crypt (next to the Wagon, Use Pile of Dirt)
* Go to the Grave south east, use Pile of dirt near the gravestone, Kill npc
* loot Hammer.

* Go back to Tiron Fordring, turn in quest / accept next part.
* go all the way to Lights Hope.
* Turn in quest. 
* Turn in Scourgestones by Duke Nicholas, (SAVE AT LEAST 1 VALOR TOKEN! )
* take Items from the Mail (Dark Iron, Savage Frond, Core of Elements)

* Find a nightelves named: Rayne, accept quest -> turn in 30 Savage Frond
* In the chapel: find Huntsman Leopold: accept quest, turn in Crypt Parts
* In the chapel: find Korfax, Champion .. : accept quest, turn in Dark Iron.
* In the chapel: find Archmage: accept quest, turn in Core of Elements
* In the chapel: find Rohan: accept quest, Turn in Bone Fragments.
* Go north Loot underwater, the Flag
* Go all the way West to Tirion Fordring, turn in quest accept next part "Of Love and Family"

* Go south to the Island, Turn in quest, SKIP NEXT PART (DUNGEON)
* HS TO UNDERCITY
* BANK PUT: ALL Crypt Fiend Parts, Savage Fronds, Core of Elements + Insignias
* go to Guild Creation, turn in "Better Late Than Never", accept "The Jeremiah Blues"
* Cockroach Vendor (68, 44), turn in "The Jeremiah Blues", accept "Good Luck Charm"
* Find Harbinger Balthazad, accept all quests.
* LEAVE undercity, Go to the Bulwark!

* Turn in Quests: Accept: A Plague Upon Thee + All Along the Watchtowers
* Go into the Western Plaguelands

* Go up the House, Turn in Quest, Accept next part
* Go on the Field Kill / Loot Jabbering Ghoul,
* Use Dropped Item in inventory.
* Go back into the House, turn in quest.
* go NorthEast

* Kill Diseased Wolfs (8)
* into the house (lumber mill), on a crate place Termite, klick on termite barrel, complete quest
* go north East and accept quest.

* Go south, Kill Knights and Mages
* Go a bit south, kill Hunter and Medics
* Go back turn in Quest.

* Kill Huntsman Radley + Durgen
* turn in Quest, Accept next part.
* go up the way until u reached the Elite Area.
* Go up the Tower * Look North way, Quest should be trigged by now.
* Go back and turn in Quest.

* Turn in quest at the Dead Tauren, Accept next part.
* Kill bears, East side,
* go back turn in Quest, Accept Next part
* go south

* Go into the House, Turn in quest, Accept next part
* go on the Graveyard Look for the Momentum grave, Interact, Turn in Quest, Accept next part
* Enter Ruins of Andorhal

* Go into the First Tower, Kill Elite, Use Torch from Inv
* Go to the next tower West, Kill elite use Torch, 
* Go into the INN (BLUE, NorthWest), on the topFloor turn in quest, accept all other quests.
* GO to the CityHall Loot Tome, Only on is the correct Tome
* The actual Annals of Darrowshire book looks different from the others (brighter)
* Go North to the 3rd Tower, Kill Elite use Torch
* Go North to the 4rd Tower, Kill Elite use Torch
* Use Temporal Displacer, on the SILO with the Blue Rays, kill mobs. (RED)

* go back to the INN, turn in Quests
* Accept "Counting Out Time" + "Brother Carlin"
* Look around the Ruins for lockboxes , in every building ruin is at least one, loot
* after 5 collected, go back to Chromie in the INN, Turn in Quest, Keep the Reward for later.
* DON'T Accept the quest again (NO EXP).
* Go back to The BULWARK!

* Turn in Quests
* accept: "Scholomance" + "Alas Andorhal"
* Turn in Scholomance accept: "Skeletal Fragments"
* Go back to Ruins of Andorhal
* farm until u have the 15 Skeletal Fragments, also Kill Araj the Summoner / loot shard
* Go back to the Bulwark, Turn in quests.
* GO to Orgrimmar

* BIND URSELF IN OG
* BANK PUT:  Bone Fragments, Scourgestones, Extended Annals of Darrowshire
* BANK GET: Umi's Mechanical Yeti, Encased Corrupt Ooze
* if npc (Cenarion Emissary Blackhoof), front of wind rider tower exists, 
** accept quest: Taking Back Silithus
* Fly to Thunderbluff.
steps.tips: * u can Donate Cloth by Orc and Troll if u didn't do that already

steps.description:
* Go East to the, Elders Rise, Turn in Quests. Accept: Rabine Saturna
* Fly to Moonglade.
steps.tips:
* u can donate cloth if u have any over.
*

steps.description:
* Turn in Quest, Accept ALL Other quests (2)
* Port back to OG
* Fly to Feralas
* Turn in Quests, SKIP Everything
* fly to Gadgetzan, Tanaris
* use the Umi's Yeti Item on Springke (NW, Gadgetzan), in front of a wagon.
* Fly TO Marshal's Refuge, Un'Goro Crater

* Use Umi's Yeti Item on "Quixxil"
* Use barrel(Encased Corrupt Ooze) on Primal Ooze (Brone slime)
* Kill Giant mob / loot item
* go to Silithus

* at the Entrance of Silithus, Turn in quest, Accept new Quest.+
* Go to Cenarion Hold

* accept: "Securing the Supply Lines" from Windcaller Proudhorn
* wanted Poster accept.
* Inn accept "Deadly Desert Venom".
* in front of the tent, near the flight master: accept "The Twilight Mystery" 
* Behind the moonwell, accept "Secret Communication" 
* From the Orc: accept "Report to General Kirika"
* in the Builden, the nightElve: accept "Dearest Natalia"

* Go Southeast, Kill all mobs there, 
* loot Dusty Reliquary (63, 55)
* Go North East if finished.

* Turn in Quest, next part
* GO back
* Go up the Tower, Click on the  Hive'Ashi Pod, then kill/loot the Hive'Ashi Ambushers 
* Loot Encrusted Silithid Object
* Keep Grinding until Brann Bronzebeard's Lost Letter Drops
* accept quest.
* Go NorthEast (Silithus Entrance) Turn in quest, Accept next part.

* Kill Spiders, Scorpions, Worms + Air Elementals
* Go north East to the Cultits Kill/Loot Encrypted Texts.
* Grind at least 20 Texts!
* Air Elementals must not be finished by now.
* Go back to Cenarion Hold.

* in Front if the INN Turn in Quest: "Securing the Supply Lines"; accept "Stepping Up Security"
* In the INN  turn in "Deadly Desert Venom".  Accept "Noggle's Last Hope"
* Behind the Moonwell: turn in Secret Communications.
* Leave NorthWest.
steps.tips: * Keep at least 10 Encrypted Text in your inventory!

steps.description:
* Kill Air Elementals Loot ALL Tablet Fragments (E)
* Kill 20 Dredge Crusher (D)
* Kill also (D) Pincer Scorpits
* Go South East

* Turn in "Report to General Kirika", accept "Scouring the Desert" 
** looks like a glowing red thing
* Go south

* Turn in Quest,
* talk to Rutgar, (long talk)
* talk to Frankal (long talk)
* Finish Noggles quest by kill/loot Scorpits / Spiders

* go north to Cenarion Hold.
* Turn in All Quests:
* Accept only: "Noggle's Lost Satchel" + "The Deserter"

* Go South East, into the Cave, Turn in Quest, accept next part.
